               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) ልፋፈ፡ጽድቅ“Bandlet of Righteousness” (pp. <locus target="#3"/>- <locus target="#29"/>), not exactly the same text as in MS Cod. <locus target="#7"/>
                     </p>
                     <p>II) ጸሎተ፡ መንገደ፡ሰማይ“Prayer of the Journey to Heaven” (pp. <locus target="#29"/>
                        <locus from="31" to="46"/>)</p>
                     <p>III) ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ሕማማተ፡መስቀሉ፡ለክርስቶስ “Prayer about the Sufferings of Our Lord on the Cross”, a story revealed to Mary Magdalen, Salome and Elizabeth (pp. <locus from="46" to="48"/>); a version of the apocryphal “Story of the Passions of Christ”, see Piovanelli <locus target="#2014"/>esp. p. <locus target="#613"/>and footnote <locus target="#18"/>; Piovanelli <locus target="#2015"/>; not exactly the same text as in Cod. Etiop. Add. <locus target="#17"/>.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
               </msContents>
