                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <p>P. <locus target="#3"/>:  በስመ፡አብ፡"…መጽሐፈ፡ሕይወት፡ወመድኃኒት፡ዘስሙ፡ልፋፈ፡ጽድቅ፡ዘጸሐፈ፡አብ፡በእደዊሁ፡ቅዱሳት፡እምቅድመ፡ይትፈጠሩ፡ሰማያት፡ወምድር፡እምቅድመ፡ነፈሳት፡ወእሳት፡ወእምቅድመ፡ሰማያት፡ወጽልመት፡ወእምቅድመ፡ብርሃናት፡ወመላእክ(p. <locus target="#4"/>)ት፡ወእምቅድመ፡ ይሳረር፡..</p>
                           
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
                  <bindingDesc>
                     <binding contemporary="true">
                        <decoNote xml:id="b1">
                           <p>The manuscript is an “accordion book” (sǝnsul) composed of three folded parchment strips (pp. <locus target="#1"/>-<locus target="#15"/>
                              <locus from="16" to="28"/> and <locus target="#29"/>of the length <locus target="#79"/>.<locus target="#6 #70"/>.<locus target="#3"/>and <locus target="#4"/>.<locus target="#5"/>cm, resp.).</p>
                           <p>Two wooden boards sewn to the first and last parchment segments on two pairs of sewing stations.  </p>
                           
                        </decoNote>
                     </binding>
                  </bindingDesc>
